🚀 PyMDP Example 2: Comprehensive Bayes Rule with VFE & PyMDP Integration
================================================================================
This example demonstrates PyMDP's VFE-based approach to Bayesian inference.
Key concepts: VFE, complexity, accuracy, sequential updating, surprise
✨ NEW: Direct PyMDP inference validation and Agent class integration

PHASE 1: Educational VFE-Based Implementations
